{
  "stem": "15645.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I was working in a-- in a farm around the time that the German come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, this was before they destroyed the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I used to work still in the German when they come in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One day, they collect-- I didn't see them because I was in the field, but later on when I come in the-- in the-- in the-- into town, they told me it was a group of German SS who it was.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- they took the-- the men-- only man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took over 100 men And between all the men was my-- my-- my wife's father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- he-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and yes, and they took them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took them, and they-- and they rode.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and they shoot them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Later on, I saw the-- the peasant with carriages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- they-- they carried the bodies in the carriages somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know where they took them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just went the come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just-- it was-- '42, I think it was. '41, '42, yes, when they start organize the ghetto, and they surround the ghetto with-- with wire.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and this time, I was in field, and I come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the road when I go back, some-- some citizen sitting and told me, don't go there, because the ghetto is surrounded.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they-- they shoot everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't go there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, in the ghetto a few months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I take to work, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was-- was-- the Germans didn't take too to do work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was working somewhere for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And still, the whole-- the whole structure of the-- of the work was the same.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, everybody was going on before to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
